THE BATTLE IN THE HIGHDEM MOUNTAINS
unlock: Access to Dr. Meade
Agrippa vs Lt.Sheeran: Lt. Sheeran has overwhelming speed, superb reflexes (attack timing), and firepower; Agrippa has one-hit kill ability and fast wits
Lt. Sheeran encounters Gen. Agrippa in the HighDem Access tunnels, with superior numbers
